Our ProductsAgriculture relies on our most precious resource: the earth. The products and tools we bring to market give consideration to environmental implications, because we have only one planet and it needs protection. 



[unex_ce_basic_banner_landing layer-name="banner - landing" layout="align-center-left" has_overlay="no-overlay" cutout_image="" cutout_image_filename="Upload Image" cutout_layout="align-bottom" id="content_9b2ntpbg1" post_id="18" semplice_styles_background_color="transparent" semplice_styles_background_image="https://monsanto.com/app/uploads/2017/03/products_banner.jpg" semplice_styles_background_size="auto" semplice_styles_background_position="50% 0%" semplice_styles_background_repeat="no-repeat" semplice_styles_padding_top="0px" semplice_styles_padding_bottom="0px" semplice_styles_padding_left="0" semplice_styles_padding_right="0"]
Our ProductsAgriculture relies on our most precious resource: the earth. The products and tools we bring to market give consideration to environmental implications, because we have only one planet and it needs protection.
[/ce_basic_banner_landing]
Our obligations extend not just to farmers, but to consumers and ecosystems around the world. Monsanto products are:Best in ClassWe believe in pursuing worthwhile innovations because our customers deserve the best tools available.SafeOur products are among the most-tested in the world and their safety has been confirmed by third-party experts and regulatory agencies.SustainableWe ensure that our contribution to the world’s food production system is sustainable, and we reduce environmental impact wherever we can.






Asgrow®




DEKALB®




Deltapine®




Monsanto Traits




Roundup®




Seminis®


See the Monsanto Products List

