Student OpportunitiesTwenty years from now, the Earth will need 55% more food than it can produce now. This means we need the next generation of bright minds engaged in our industry. We look for talented students currently enrolled in full-time bachelor’s, master’s, and PhD programs to fill our internships and co-ops, and trainee programs where many go on to hold full-time jobs at Monsanto.Learn About Student Opportunities 



