Monsanto Facilities Around the WorldMonsanto is headquartered in St. Louis, Missouri, in the United States, and has locations around the world. Our administrative and sales offices, manufacturing plants, seed production facilities, research centers, and learning centers are all part of the corporate focus on agriculture and supporting farmers.By having locations close to our customers, we are better able to fulfill their needs, understand the pressures they face and develop tailored innovations.For information about Monsanto locations, select the country of interest from the list. 
