Stewardship of Financial ResourcesEvery person needs a farmer every day. And every farmer needs tools and solutions every season. As the world continues to grow, the potential for our products grow with it.  Today our seed technologies alone reach more than 400 million acres of corn, soybeans, cotton, and vegetables and have the potential to serve many more. We firmly believe helping farmers grow the world’s food, feed, fuel, and fiber will continued to be a timeless and relevant business model.Presentations and Financial ReportsSEC Filings Stock PerformanceInvestor EventsShareowner InformationDividend History 



