Our BusinessThis globally minded, sustainably driven mission’s intent is to deliver innovative products that deliver strong returns for farmers and investors alike. We invest more than $1.5 billion annually in R&D to deliver high-performing seeds and digital ag tools that improve productivity, reduce costs for farmers, and produce better food for consumers and feed for animals.Contact Investor RelationsLearn More About Monsanto 




